Slackware $sysname ${color3}$kernel$color ${machine}${font}
${color3}${execi 9000 whoami}$color @ $nodename ${alignr}Desktop ${color3}${desktop}$color of ${desktop_number}
${color3}Uptime:${color} $uptime_short

